RACE.RACE_TEXT: Autumn Derby Trial GRANTS PASS RACE 1 400 Y Dirt CR: 78. Derby Trial Purse 5000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS WHICH REMAIN ELIGIBLE FOR THE AUTUMN DERBY. Final Purse $20,000 plus nomination fees. Final to be run on October 9, 2023. Weight, 125 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: DASH TO THE FLASH T broke sharp, best. GOOD CANDY CASH drifted out, game for place. LL LIL FAVORITELOVER drifted in, willingly for show. FLAGSTAFF in tight. JESS BE GENUINE hopped at break.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: Autumn Derby Trial GRANTS PASS RACE 2 400 Y Dirt CR: 85. Derby Trial Purse 5000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS WHICH REMAIN ELIGIBLE FOR THE AUTUMN DERBY. Final Purse $20,000 plus nomination fees. Final to be run on October 9, 2023. Weight, 125 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BEE A FREIGHT TRAIN dueled, pulled away. WHISKEY DIVA dueled early, game for place. DASH FOR FIVE T rallied. CHISUM steadied. JESS AFTER MIDNITE mild effort. ANNIES CHOICE outside effort.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: GRANTS PASS RACE 3 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 80. Claiming Purse 7200. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE IN 2023. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs. Claiming Price $3,200 (Maiden, Claiming, Or Starter Races For $2,500 Or Less Not Considered In Eligibility)(Races at OR Fairs or WA Class C Tracks Not Considered in Eligibility).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FAMOUS ROCK STAR held a pressured pace throughout, continued rally for win. DARK AND DANDY stalked pace, moved up outside in stretch for place. MISO FAST chased pace. SECRET LIFE STYLE bid late between foes. NATIONHEART raced middle of pack. PRINCE OF LUCK forced early pace, weakened. SMOKE AND BURN settled off pace.
